hcc_text: Harlem River Driveway is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Manhattan)
info: At Harlem River Driveway at West 155th Street, St. Nicholas Place and Edgecombe Avenue, there were 6 severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
intersection: Harlem River Driveway at West 155th Street, St. Nicholas Place and Edgecombe Avenue
